cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.MM 

This paper is about human parsing, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category. The paper also discusses the use of deep graph networks and message-passing networks, which are common in machine learning and artificial intelligence, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) a likely category as well. The paper also focuses on modeling human structures, which involves natural language processing and understanding, making cs.CL (Computation and Language) a possible category. Finally, the paper discusses experiments on five datasets, which suggests that cs.MM (Multimedia) could also be a relevant category.
